</P>
<P>
   INTERNET-AUCTIONS (Undated) _ Internet auctions are promoted for
their ability to rid the world of middlemen and let buyers and
sellers strike deals in free-market harmony. But as auction sites
look to cash in on the trend by selling more costly goods, this
Internet utopia is coming under threat. Higher prices can mean
lower levels of trust. By Bob Tedeschi.
</P>
