   ANONYMOUS-EMAIL (Cambridge, Mass.) _ At MIT, a debate over the
ethics of so-called anonymous remailers _ network server computers
than enable people to transmit E-mail that is anonymous and
virtually untraceable. By Steve Lohr.
</P>
