   KOSOVO-ALBANIA (Tirana) _ A refugee family, trying to cross the
border, veered into a mine in the dark, killing 5 and injuring 2.
The border has been closed and reopened twice since, but the
refugee flow has grown greatly. By Anthony DePalma.
</P>
