hard. Powell, who had five ancestors fight for the Confederate
States of America, is going to every city and county in Florida,
urging leaders to recognize April as Confederate Memorial month.
He's spent his adylt life fighting the stereotype that the
Confederacy was only about slavery. (Kleinberg, Palm Beach Post)
