<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-18 20:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3347 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NY-AMBULANCES-2TAKES-     04-18 1215
