<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Y2KWATCH-Y2KWATCH </SLUG>
 _ SF CHRON  
 Protecting Credit Against Perils of Y2K
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; By Benny Evangelista &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; c 1999, San Francisco Chronicle &QL;  &LR; 
