form a union. On the same weekend, Harvard University held a
conference which focused on creating a nationwide student-labor
alliance to build on recent anti-sweatshop demonstrations on
campuses. Students from both universities say they hope to use
their voice to help unions on a variety of issues. (George Ruhe/New
