Pittsburgh Penguins 2-1 in overtime. After the game, the Great One
who shattered hockey's most revered records skated one lap around
the rink with his teammates in tow, followed by an encore. ``I'm
going to miss this game,'' he said to his teammates. ``It's going
to kill me not to play.'' (Barton Silverman/New York Times Photo)
